"[Baia Mare Planetarium](planetariul_bm@yahoo.com), as a result of a project\n"
"called _Traditional Romanian Constellations_ developed in 2012-2013 by the \n"
"[Baia Mare Planetarium](https://www.planetariubm.ro)\n"
